name: Dies Irae -1
description:
Dies Irae, the judgment day, represents multiples scenarios of the results of a war, abandoned cities, death, debris, in summary sad places, places in which there is no life, in which life has taken life by its egoism and lack of communication. In the canvas there is only one scenario with life, at the bottom right you can see how life and order always manage to find its way between chaos. There are a positive and negative piece.

Dimensions: 2000x1234 Pixels

Tools used: GLIDE, image editor
